data.description:
Assumable FHA rate at 3.25%. must meet FHA criteria and have the money to pay the difference but it's a great way to get a lower rate in this market.  Beautiful waterfront property that has all the charm and is an entertainers dream. NEW ROOF 2021!.  Home is great for entertaining with the huge back deck and open floor plan. Has a bonus room with plumbing that can be added on for an apartment. SELLER IS WILLING TO DO 4% INTEREST RATE FOR BOND FOR DEED WITH ACCEPTABLE TERMS.  

Home has 2 dishwashers, wine fridge, 2 on demand water heaters, whole house generator, 1 year old steam shower, push button microwave, auto underground sprinkler, security system, 3 AC systems (2 down 1 up), speaker system in the middle of the home. attic upstairs plumbed for addition if wanted, plantation shutters on every window, 2 attics for storage, pull out drawers for pots in kitchen. Home was completely gutted and renovated after Katrina so it has all newer wiring etc. There is a community boat launch. Just minutes from amazing private school Lake Castle, interstate, shopping and hospitals.
